DAT
id=qid::label=str::text=lstr::
5591::$$$message_0051_0000_0000$$$::Hello!!! Is everyone doing good?::
5592::$$$message_0051_0000_0001$$$::Good players should only play an hour of games per day! Anyway, this is Tiger Dojo, your helpful segment that deals punishing blows to those who died pathetically, while also solving all your problems, just like that!::
5593::$$$message_0051_0000_0002$$$::Anyway, this whole segment does seem to do a complete one-eighty from the rest of the game, so what's the point!?[lr]::
5594::$$$message_0051_0000_0003$$$::Answer, Disciple Number One!::
5595::$$$message_0051_0000_0004$$$::Yes, ma'am! This dojo is a behind-the-scenes segment to help out that dimwit Shirou... That means this is the pillar that supports [font italic=true]Fate[font italic=false]!::
5596::$$$message_0051_0000_0005$$$::It may be no exaggeration that THIS is the main story of [font italic=true]Fate[font italic=false]! ::
5597::$$$message_0051_0000_0006$$$::Marvelous! Bravo...avocado!::
5598::$$$message_0051_0000_0007$$$::Very good. Anyway...you may have realized this by now, but this dojo itself is [font italic=true]Fate's[font italic=false] very core.::
5599::$$$message_0051_0000_0008$$$::Don't you get tricked by those fake heroines acting all high and mighty in the main story, and if you see any choice that seems even a little suspicious, don't hesitate to choose that one!::
5600::$$$message_0051_0000_0009$$$::Anyway. This time, Shirou...::
5601::$$$message_0051_0000_0010$$$::Aw man. He got squished real good![lr]::
5602::$$$message_0051_0000_0011$$$::Who does that kind of thing? Must be a real jerk! What do you think about that, my disciple?::
5603::$$$message_0051_0000_0012$$$::I don't see a problem! That's clearly a cute, hip way for someone to express a twisted kind of love!::
5604::$$$message_0051_0000_0013$$$::WRONG!::
5605::$$$message_0051_0000_0014$$$::Ouch... M-my mistake. Anyway, this time around, the hopeless Shirou met his end because he ticked off a certain heroine.::
5606::$$$message_0051_0000_0015$$$::Exactly. He shamelessly broke the honorable samurai spirit by showing his back to the enemy. He committed a literal seppuku...a suicide by disembowelment.::
5607::$$$message_0051_0000_0016$$$::So from now on, make sure you choose looots of cowardly choices. You'll have no trouble dying again.::
5608::$$$message_0051_0000_0017$$$::But, you know, this [font italic=true]is[font italic=false] a Q&A segment by name, so I suppose I need to listen to your problems.[lr]::
5609::$$$message_0051_0000_0018$$$::Disciple Number One. What is the appropriate countermeasure for this?::
5610::$$$message_0051_0000_0019$$$::Ma'am, yes, ma'am! You need to go back to the branching choices and choose the other one!::
5611::$$$message_0051_0000_0020$$$::Yep, very good![lr]::
5612::$$$message_0051_0000_0021$$$::Unexpected deaths like this happen all the time, so saving right before you make a selection should be standard practice.::
5613::$$$message_0051_0000_0022$$$::That's it for this time! I'll see you at the next practice!::
5614::$$$message_0051_0000_0023$$$::Yep! See ya!::

